.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, daisy, orchid
1. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Flower   | iris      | azalea   | daisy | orchid  |

