.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pear, corn, cherry
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person eating pear and the person eating broccoli##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person eating pear is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food         | corn | broccoli   | cherry | pear |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

