.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, tiparillo, davidoff, alhambra
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the nigerian is somewhere between the american and the dutch##7
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar      | tiparillo | havana      | davidoff | alhambra     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

