.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, techno, hip-hop, metal
1. the argentine is not the fan of metal##6
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
3. the spanish is the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Music-Genre           | hip-hop   | metal    | dubstep       | techno  |

