.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
House: farmhouse, palace, cape-cod, tower
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the tower house is somewhere between the farmhouse house and the owner of the snake##7
2. the palace house is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the cape-cod house##6
4. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the farmhouse house is the owner of the dog##1
6. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| House   | farmhouse | tower | palace | cape-cod |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

