2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the tower house is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | card-games | woodworking | writing |
| House   | tower  | cape-cod    | futuristic    | ranch-style  |

