2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the owner of the snake##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the owner of the snake is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| Pet   | turtle   | mouse      | snake        | fish  |

