3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
