3. the paramedic is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the van is not the paramedic##6
5. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the architect and the freelancer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Transport   | car | bus     | taxi     | van |
| Job     | paramedic | freelancer | firefighter | architect     |

