2. the person drinking tea is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage    | fanta   | lemonade  | tea  | soy-milk |
