.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, brown, white, azure
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, documentary, drama, horror
1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
3. the person who likes brown is not the person watching documentary movies##6
4. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person who likes brown##7
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Color           | brown | white  | chestnut  | azure |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | horror | documentary | drama   |

