4. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the trike is not the old-henry-smoker##6
6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the fonseca-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
